":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dec23eb6bce2381c2453367246e7e22d112ca9c","tid":1780812,"uid":328199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">休樓豬老母</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗下死咗嘅手足你條仆街仲會唔會想休<br />\n休一日死多幾多人仆你個街<br />\n你休敵人唔會休<br />\n手足繼續死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"大部分示威者都必須有休息，問題點樣休息，令大家復出時最團結、最有力量。<br />\n<br />\n最理想係休息本身已經爭取到戰果。<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢無休息超過7天，日日只食黃店，純粹為大局思考。"},{"pid":"041f09abdc38b4a4cba647cd495419d238be342d","tid":1780812,"uid":72693,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n平時已經休咗六日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da074905b8db37c5711c08a0682f9c12d907f375","tid":1780812,"uid":36578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:08:15.000Z","msg":"準備攻狗屋，休你老母"},{"pid":"0e629504767963edb90229e92f1238aedb0115a2","tid":1780812,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"休你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14880d257e77b9e17c0fa7cc5a3e931702cf226d","tid":1780812,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"又休 10月頭又係有堆P牌三毛打手叫休息 <br />\n你咁撚鐘意休唔該你走上前線幫手擋下 鐘意喺臭格休又得醫院休又得"},{"pid":"11450fc4da3b6a4132e86259def1006d4c9c2248","tid":1780812,"uid":27511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"745d3520df1283f21c3c4f37a8dc60acd36fab9e","tid":1780812,"uid":134704,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"你要休息就去休 <br />\n休息返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我行住等你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"啱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\